  <brief_title>The Effect of Beer, Red Wine and Fruit Juice on Blood Vessel Function in Persons With Cardiovascular Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Alcohol and Polyphenolic Compounds on Endothelial Function</official_title>
  <sponsors>
